<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Error — LF Dropship</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; background: #0f1117; color: #e2e8f0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; min-height: 100vh; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    h1 { color: #ff5f5f; font-size: 1.5rem; }
    pre { background: #1a1d27; padding: 1rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #2e3148; font-size: 0.8rem; max-width: 600px; white-space: pre-wrap; word-break: break-word; color: #8892b0; }
    a { color: #6c63ff; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>⚠️ <%= message %></h1>
